data.title: Great Pizza, 50/50 service
data.text: The pizza is great but the service is not consistent. I order pizza from this location a lot.I usually order online but I also use the mobile app. I order two pizzas last time, one with light sauce and the other with normal sauce. I received two pizzas with light sauce. I did state this on their website but didn't leave my contact information. I didn't feel like the bother. The pizza was still good.

data.title: Domino's
data.text: Speedy delivery and courteous driver. The foods was very delicious and hot at delivery. I loved being able to monitor my order online.
